DomainData.MainText: Nofoaga Autu e Filifili ai le Le Faalauaiteleina
DomainData.MainInfoText: Pe a e asiasi i soo se uepisaite, e mafai ona teu pe toe aumai faamatalaga i luga o lau palausa, e tele lava i le ituaiga o kuki. O lenei faamatalaga atonu e faatatau ia te oe, o mea e te manao i ai po o lau masini ma e tele lava ina faaaoga e fai ai le saite e pei ona e faamoemoe i ai. E le masani ona faailoa sa'o mai oe e faamatalaga, ae e mafai ona e maua ai se aafiaga e sili atu ona patino i le uepi. Talu ai matou te faaaloalo i lau aia tatau i le le faalauaiteleina, e mafai ona e filifili e aua nei faatagaina nisi o ituaiga o kuki. Kiliki i ulutala o vaega eseese e iloa ai nisi mea ma sui ai a tatou faatulagaga masani. Ae peitai, o le polokaina o nisi o ituaiga o kuki e ono aafia ai lou aafiaga i le saite ma auaunaga e mafai ona tatou ofoina atu.
DomainData.AlertNoticeText: E ala i le kilikiina o le "Accept All Cookies", ua e ioe ai i le teuina o kuki i luga o lau masini e faaleleia ai le faatautaia o le saite, iloilo le faaaogaina o le saite, ma fesoasoani i a tatou taumafaiga faamaketi.

DomainData.CookieListDescription: O se kuki o se vaega itiiti o faamatalaga (faila o faamatalaga) lea e i ai se uepisaite – pe a asiasi atu i ai se tagata faaaoga – fai atu i lau palausa e teu i luga o lau masini ina ia manatua ai faamatalaga e uiga ia te oe, e pei o le mea e manao i ai lau gagana po o faamatalaga e alu ai i totonu. O na kuki e setiina e i matou ma ta'ua o kuki o le vaega muamua. Matou te faaaogaina foi kuki o le vaega lona tolu – o ni kuki mai se vaega e ese mai le vaega o le uepisaite o loo e asiasi i ai – mo a matou taumafaiga o faasalalauga ma maketi. E patino lava, tatou te faaaogaina kuki ma isi tekinolosi e siaki ai mo faamoemoega nei:

O lenei kuki e faaaoga e iloagofie ai tagata faaaoga tulaga ese e ala i le atofaina atu o se numera na otometi ona faagaoioia o se tagata e iloa ai le tagata. O loo aofia ai i le talosaga mo itulau taitasi i se saite ma e faaaoga e fuafua ai tagata asiasi, faamatalaga o sauniga ma faatosinaga mo lipoti a le saite o loo faaaogaina. FirstPartyCookies.thirdPartyDescription: This cookie is set by the Google Analytics and determines new sessions and visits.  It expires after 30 minutes. The cookie is updated every time data is sent to Google Analytics. Any activity by a user within the 30 minute life span will count as a single visit, even if the user leaves and then returns to the site. A return after 30 minutes will count as a new visit, but a returning visitor.
FirstPartyCookies.Name: __utmb
FirstPartyCookies.description: O se tasi lenei o kuki autu e fa na faatulagaina e le Google Analytics o le auaunaga lea e mafai ai e tagata o le uepisaite ona siaki le behaviour o tagata asiasi ma le fuaina o le faatinoga o le saite. O lenei kuki e fuafua ai sauniga fou ma asiasiga ma faamutaina pe a mavae le 30 minute. E faafouina ia kuki i taimi uma e auina atu ai faamaumauga i le Google Analytics. Soo se gaoioiga a se tagata faaaoga i totonu o le 30 minute o le olaga, o le a faitauina o se asiasiga se tasi, e tusa lava pe o laulaau o le tagata e faaaogaina ona toe foi lea i le saite. O se toe foi mai pe a mavae le 30 minute o le a faitauina o se asiasiga fou, ae o se tagata asiasi ua toe foi mai.

FirstPartyCookies.thirdPartyDescription: This cookie is set by the Google Analytics and is used to calculate new and returning visitor statistics.   It is not used in most sites but is set to enable interoperability with the older version of Google Analytics code known as Urchin.  In this older versions this was used in combination with the __utmb cookie to identify new sessions/visits for returning visitors.  When used by Google Analytics this is always a Session cookie which is destroyed when the user closes their browser.
FirstPartyCookies.Name: __utmc
FirstPartyCookies.description:
O se tasi lenei o kuki autu e fa ua setiina e le tautua a le Google I totonu o le uepisaite lea e mafai ai e i latou e anaina le uepisaite ona tulituliloaina ia amioga a tagata asiasi ma fuaina le faatinoga o saite. E le o faaaogaina i le tele o saite ae ua seti ina ia mafai ai ona le fesootai ma le faaaogaina o fesootaiga ma le lomiga tuai o le numera faailo a le Google, e igoa o le Urchin.  I lenei lomiga tuai sa faaaogaina faatasi ai lenei mea ma le kuki __utmb e faailoa mai ai sauniga/asiasiga fou mo tagata asiasi mai.
Pe a faaaogaina e le GoogleS o se kuki lea o le Sauniga lea e faaleagaina pe a tapuni e le tagata e faaaogaina le palausa. O le mea e iloa atu ai o se cookie Finafinau o le mea lea e foliga mai ai o se isi lava tekinolosi e setiina le kuki.
